					<article>
						<p>separate contacts page seems to be THE solution, but there are many spiders who don&#8217;t use (ignore) robots.txt.</p>
<p>You could appeal to human intelligence and wrote your email in some weird way still readable to human willing to contact you:</p>
<p>your.name # domaain tld<br />
or<br />
your DOT name AT NOSPAM DOT domain DOT tld&#8230;</p>
